com.thinkaurelius.titan.graphdb.internal

Class AbstractElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thinkaurelius.titan.graphdb.internal.AbstractElement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Idfiable, TitanElement, InternalElement, Removable, Comparable<TitanElement>, org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Element
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractTypedRelation, AbstractVertex

    public abstract class AbstractElement
extends Object
implements InternalElement, Comparable<TitanElement>
    AbstractElement is the base class for all elements in Titan. It is defined and uniquely identified by its id.

    For the id, it holds that: id<0: Temporary id, will be assigned id>0 when the transaction is committed id=0: Virtual or implicit element that does not physically exist in the database id>0: Physically persisted element
    Author:
    Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
